{
  "stem": "11611.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, of course I contradicted him, but I didn't carry on a prolonged argument with him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just told the Swiss that was the last time he was coming to that house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the case, they didn't bring him again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not to begin with.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I say, I was assigned to-- it was a make work job for about a month to read the transcripts and pick out evidentiary rulings and to prepare a manual on procedure and evidence.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, it must have been 100, 150 pages of various rulings here, there, and everywhere, disputes about translation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The prosecution lawyers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, he was effectively Jackson's successor as the head of the American group, and very able, very able.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jackson was able too, but I'm talking about Taylor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was assigned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was assigned to a tentative, projected case against German banks, plural, particularly the Dresdner and Deutsche Banks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Deutsche was the largest bank in Germany, Dresdner was the second largest bank.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were working up a case against a fellow named Hermann Abs, who was a very famous German banker, good connections with Lehman Brothers, and a case against a couple of board members of the Dresdner Bank who were also SS officers and Friends of Himmler.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I say friends of Himmler, there was a circle called the Friends of Himmler and they were members of the circle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Dresdner Bank and the Deutsche Bank completed in taking over Jewish properties, either before or after their owners were killed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, they were ghouls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can get more into that, but anyhow, I worked together with a couple of other lawyers.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
